{"tid":920541,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"(WhatsApp group)又係時候準備2019年","createTime":"2018-11-29T01:28:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T03:50:40.000Z","uid":9178,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3c13266d0c7079a972c79e71c7679fe13eacbb41","tid":920541,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T01:28:34.000Z","msg":"歡迎任何正係想吹水嘅人入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩想講可以講 唔洗驚要出嚟真人面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為你嘅WhatsApp 增添熱鬧氣息<br />\n唔驚冇人搵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n主要都係吹水多 <br />\ngroup 聚除非真係有人想出/唔出唔得先搞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嚴禁厹 5p 殘體 <br />\n潛水 非活躍份子必踢 <br />\n入嚟係到睇冇咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加人速度慢 有意填表<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/fHcsljSMjoWaTE5l2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FfHcsljSMjoWaTE5l2&d=8%2F8z883Pf3IVZkbh3r2cI%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=576c8f82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/fHcsljSMjoWaTE5l2</a><br />\n<br />\n期待你嘅出現 為group中帶嚟好傾嘅話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5bd532601d7afdc091dfe9aa6b3975411286f7a","tid":920541,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T03:47:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5aac64d99d1d3be101ae90a97e21b567b6a24d8","tid":920541,"uid":16096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:24:05.000Z","msg":"有幾多人而家"},{"pid":"202243cdc59d984cb375241acc89c21f2c235231","tid":920541,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5aac64d99d1d3be101ae90a97e21b567b6a24d8","tid":920541,"uid":16096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:24:05.000Z","msg":"有幾多人而家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"